Hot 100 Chart:
1. Roddy Ricch - "The Box"

4. The Weeknd - "Blinding Lights"

Billboard 200 Chart:
1. Lil Uzi Vert - "Eternal Atake" (New Entry)
2. Jhene Aiko - "Chilombo" (New Entry)
3. Bad Bunny - "YHLQMDLG"
4. Lil Baby - "My Turn"

Artist 100 Chart:
1. Lil Uzi Vert
2. NCT 127
3. Jhene Aiko
4. BTS
5. Post Malone

Interesting Notes:
- Lil Uzi Vert dominated the charts, topping both the Billboard 200 and Artist 100 charts
- Several new albums made strong debuts, including Eternal Atake and Chilombo
- The Hot 100 showed a mix of hip-hop, pop, and R&B hits"}
